        "\"He who began a good work in you will carry it on to completion.\" \u{2014} Philippians 1:6\n\nYou are not finished. Neither is God. The fact that you are here proves the work is still happening. Write your response below. Honesty is strength, not weakness.",
        "\"Whoever walks with the wise becomes wise.\" \u{2014} Proverbs 13:20\n\nLook at your inner circle. Are they pulling you toward Christ or away from Him? Ask God to make this real in your life today, not just a nice idea.",
