        "\"Let all that you do be done in love.\" \u{2014} 1 Corinthians 16:14\n\nStrength without love is aggression. How will you lead with love today? How does this truth change the way you approach today?",
        "\"Create in me a clean heart, O God.\" \u{2014} Psalm 51:10\n\nDavid brought his mess to God. What do you need to bring to Him today? What would it look like to live this out in the next 24 hours?",
        "\"The righteous man falls seven times, and rises again.\" \u{2014} Proverbs 24:16\n\nFalling is not the problem. Staying down is. Get back up, brother. Today, challenge: share this with one person who needs to hear it.",
        "\"Do not be conformed to this world, but be transformed.\" \u{2014} Romans 12:2\n\nWhat is the world telling you today that contradicts what God says about you? Sit with this for 60 seconds before moving on. Let it sink in.",
        "\"Trust in the Lord with all your heart.\" \u{2014} Proverbs 3:5\n\nSelf-reliance is the quiet drift. Where are you leaning on your own understanding? Write your response below. Honesty is strength, not weakness.",
